content: Hi! Thanks - have you taken the text training with us yet?
no - i cant figure out how to take the training
when i sign up for the training it says that I am signed up but I never receive link to join the actual training
Got it - hm! Sorry about that
Can you try to sign up again https://events.democrats.org/event/672393/
And check your Spam email folder for the Zoom link
If you still don't see it (the Zoom link is usually sent the day-of the training) - let me know and I can send you the Zoom link
Thanks - i took the training and I am ready to go
Great, thanks! You should see a Direct Message (DM) from one of us in the next ~24 hours or so!
